306
00:14:45,463 --> 00:14:46,264
It's quiet.

307
00:14:46,424 --> 00:14:48,264
No tricky human connections.

308
00:14:48,544 --> 00:14:49,623
And I'm paid well.

309
00:14:49,784 --> 00:14:50,584
I don't have

310
00:14:50,584 --> 00:14:51,823
any KPIs to meet.

