313
00:14:55,743 --> 00:14:56,983
This is the perfect job

314
00:14:56,983 --> 00:14:58,664
for someone who wants to make life easy.

315
00:15:01,544 --> 00:15:02,583
Chengyi.

316
00:15:03,144 --> 00:15:04,424
You know

317
00:15:04,424 --> 00:15:05,823
I chose to go abroad

318
00:15:06,184 --> 00:15:07,784
