332
00:15:45,184 --> 00:15:46,223
That's my room.

333
00:15:52,064 --> 00:15:53,064
What do you think?

334
00:15:53,384 --> 00:15:54,463
Isn't it quite nice?

335
00:15:56,343 --> 00:15:57,823
How can a young lady

336
00:15:57,823 --> 00:15:58,785
live in a cemetery?

337
00:15:58,785 --> 00:16:00,463
Aren't you scared at night?

338
00:16:00,743 --> 00:16:02,103
Should I call you reckless

339
00:16:02,103 --> 00:16:03,223
