340
00:16:03,384 --> 00:16:04,223
It's fine.

341
00:16:04,304 --> 00:16:06,223
My master takes good care of me.

342
00:16:06,343 --> 00:16:07,145
Besides,

343
00:16:07,145 --> 00:16:08,703
