344
00:16:09,144 --> 00:16:10,024
I also have a dog

345
00:16:10,024 --> 00:16:11,024
called Yiersan.

346
00:16:15,863 --> 00:16:16,664
Chengyi.

347
00:16:16,863 --> 00:16:18,223
Believe it or not,

348
00:16:18,583 --> 00:16:20,583
I've been an insomniac for years.

349
00:16:20,863 --> 00:16:22,024
I sleep better here

350
00:16:22,223 --> 00:16:23,424
than anywhere else.

351
00:16:23,983 --> 00:16:25,103
I sleep till dawn.

352
00:16:26,904 --> 00:16:28,144
That was one of the reasons

353
00:16:28,144 --> 00:16:29,623
why I chose to work here.

354
00:16:30,103 --> 00:16:31,384
An overseas graduate

355
00:16:31,384 --> 00:16:33,384
is living a retired life here.

356
00:16:33,384 --> 00:16:34,784
What if your parents find out?

357
00:16:35,703 --> 00:16:36,703
How would they

358
00:16:37,024 --> 00:16:38,583
find out if you don't tell them?

359
00:16:42,144 --> 00:16:43,144
Chengyi.

360
00:16:44,424 --> 00:16:46,064
Dear Chengyi.

361
00:16:46,943 --> 00:16:48,384
Dearest Chengyi.

362
00:16:48,384 --> 00:16:50,664
Help me out.

363
00:16:50,664 --> 00:16:51,463
Enough.

364
00:16:51,623 --> 00:16:53,064
Straighten your tongue.

365
00:16:53,064 --> 00:16:53,744
Speak properly.

366
00:16:53,744 --> 00:16:55,024
Otherwise, I'll call Dad.

367
00:16:55,024 --> 00:16:56,024
Mei Chengyi.

368
00:16:56,343 --> 00:16:57,343
If you set me up,

369
00:16:57,343 --> 00:16:57,904
my sister

370
00:16:57,904 --> 00:16:58,904
won't let you off.

371
00:16:59,983 --> 00:17:01,904
Stop threatening me with your sister.

372
00:17:04,464 --> 00:17:06,183
I'll take it as you've agreed.

373
00:17:07,623 --> 00:17:08,623
Chengyi.

374
00:17:09,224 --> 00:17:10,224
Chengyi.

375
00:17:38,984 --> 00:17:40,343
Sorry, I fell asleep

376
00:17:40,343 --> 00:17:41,704
and caused you trouble.

377
00:17:41,984 --> 00:17:43,143
The kids are asleep.

378
00:17:43,583 --> 00:17:44,863
Hurry back to the hospital.

379
00:17:47,623 --> 00:17:49,103
Can we talk for a minute?

380
00:17:49,944 --> 00:17:50,984
You have the mood

381
00:17:50,984 --> 00:17:51,984
to talk to me?

382
00:17:53,383 --> 00:17:54,383
About what?

383
00:17:55,863 --> 00:17:57,304
About Xiaomi.

384
00:18:05,984 --> 00:18:06,984
Let's talk here.

385
00:18:09,064 --> 00:18:10,863
Okay, I'll make it short.

386
00:18:12,064 --> 00:18:13,103
I wanted to

387
00:18:13,863 --> 00:18:15,064
ask you to remarry me,

388
00:18:16,304 --> 00:18:17,704
so that you and the kids

389
00:18:17,704 --> 00:18:18,823
could have a home.

390
00:18:19,784 --> 00:18:21,504
I also couldn't let go of our past.

391
00:18:23,623 --> 00:18:24,584
But now, I realize

392
00:18:24,584 --> 00:18:25,704
that you wouldn't

393
00:18:25,704 --> 00:18:26,704
remarry me.

394
00:18:27,984 --> 00:18:28,985
You finally developed

395
00:18:28,985 --> 00:18:30,623
the self-awareness of a middle-aged man.

396
00:18:31,623 --> 00:18:32,623
Yeah.

397
00:18:33,423 --> 00:18:34,944
So now, I want

398
00:18:34,944 --> 00:18:36,343
to make a fair deal with you.

399
00:18:37,744 --> 00:18:38,744
What deal?

400
00:18:39,064 --> 00:18:40,264
I'll give back

401
00:18:41,264 --> 00:18:44,024
your apartment plus an extra

402
00:18:44,583 --> 00:18:45,704
300,000 yuan

403
00:18:45,863 --> 00:18:47,103
and I'll take Xiaomi.

404
00:18:48,183 --> 00:18:48,984
Qian Hao.

405
00:18:49,183 --> 00:18:50,304
Your shamelessness

406
00:18:50,583 --> 00:18:51,545
has gone beyond

407
00:18:51,545 --> 00:18:53,064
my wildest imagination.

408
00:18:55,183 --> 00:18:57,024
I know you find it hard to accept.

409
00:18:57,623 --> 00:18:58,863
But you know me.

410
00:18:59,064 --> 00:19:00,464
Whenever I want to do something,

411
00:19:00,464 --> 00:19:01,504
