412
00:19:02,623 --> 00:19:04,143
My mom is in ICU.

413
00:19:04,464 --> 00:19:06,264
Xiaomi is the last thread
of her attachment.

414
00:19:06,264 --> 00:19:07,863
Whatever the cost,

415
00:19:09,024 --> 00:19:10,623
I will get my son back.

416
00:19:16,143 --> 00:19:17,704
I advise you to accept my proposal,

417
00:19:18,224 --> 00:19:19,464
or you will regret it.

418
00:19:19,464 --> 00:19:21,423
I already regret it now.

419
00:19:21,744 --> 00:19:22,944
I shouldn't have brought them

420
00:19:22,944 --> 00:19:23,663
here.

421
00:19:23,663 --> 00:19:24,663
