425
00:19:30,343 --> 00:19:32,423
I can't let her die with regrets.

426
00:19:32,544 --> 00:19:33,863
We have two children.

427
00:19:33,863 --> 00:19:35,992
One for you and one for me.
It's only fair.

428
00:19:37,704 --> 00:19:38,623
What are you doing?

429
00:19:38,704 --> 00:19:39,465
You cheated on me

430
00:19:39,465 --> 00:19:40,704
