432
00:19:41,984 --> 00:19:42,744
You chose

433
00:19:42,744 --> 00:19:43,664
to ignore our kids.

434
00:19:43,664 --> 00:19:45,064
How was that fair?

435
00:19:45,064 --> 00:19:45,864
You want custody

436
00:19:45,864 --> 00:19:47,064
after Lili and I

437
00:19:47,064 --> 00:19:48,065
