439
00:19:49,863 --> 00:19:51,143
As I said, Xu Kaixin.

440
00:19:51,143 --> 00:19:52,663
Everyone makes mistakes.

441
00:19:52,663 --> 00:19:53,704
Why won't you

442
00:19:53,704 --> 00:19:54,584
give me a chance

443
00:19:54,584 --> 00:19:56,264
to make things right?

444
00:19:56,264 --> 00:19:57,264
Qian Hao.

445
00:19:58,183 --> 00:19:59,863
You won't cherish your child

446
00:19:59,863 --> 00:20:00,863
with Hu Xiaojiao

447
00:20:01,224 --> 00:20:03,064
and insist on taking my son.

448
00:20:04,064 --> 00:20:05,025
Is Hu Xiaojiao

449
00:20:05,025 --> 00:20:06,224
carrying

450
00:20:06,304 --> 00:20:07,504
someone else's child?

451
00:20:31,583 --> 00:20:33,863
Yeah, you're right.

452
00:20:34,784 --> 00:20:36,103
Hu Xiaojiao

453
00:20:37,183 --> 00:20:38,823
keeps saying she loves me,

454
00:20:39,663 --> 00:20:40,424
but she's carrying

455
00:20:40,424 --> 00:20:42,064
another man's child.

456
00:20:53,383 --> 00:20:54,144
Now you know

457
00:20:54,144 --> 00:20:55,304
my determination

458
00:20:55,304 --> 00:20:56,304
to get my son back.

459
00:20:57,583 --> 00:20:58,505
I advise you

460
00:20:58,505 --> 00:20:59,623
to think it over.

461
00:20:59,823 --> 00:21:00,863
Take the apartment.

462
00:21:01,143 --> 00:21:02,183
Then Dami and you

463
00:21:02,183 --> 00:21:03,663
won't need to rent a house.

464
00:21:03,663 --> 00:21:05,304
You'll have a place of your own.

465
00:21:05,304 --> 00:21:06,704
I'm not selling my kid.

466
00:21:07,383 --> 00:21:08,183
Also,

467
00:21:08,383 --> 00:21:09,383
I have a home.

468
00:21:09,704 --> 00:21:11,504
You're the one who doesn't have a home.

469
00:21:14,343 --> 00:21:15,544
You lonely soul.

470
00:22:56,143 --> 00:22:57,383
What's going on?

471
00:22:57,383 --> 00:22:58,903
I'm just telling her.

472
00:22:59,583 --> 00:23:00,784
Once a man and a woman

473
00:23:00,784 --> 00:23:01,744
