474
00:23:01,744 --> 00:23:02,465
they can't

475
00:23:02,465 --> 00:23:03,823
possibly sever ties.

476
00:23:04,903 --> 00:23:06,704
You didn't see how much Qian Hao tried

477
00:23:06,704 --> 00:23:08,024
to cling to them.

478
00:23:08,304 --> 00:23:10,224
You should see for yourself.

479
00:23:10,304 --> 00:23:11,225
You must stop

480
00:23:11,225 --> 00:23:12,583
deceiving yourself.

481
00:23:12,863 --> 00:23:14,143
Although his mom

482
00:23:14,143 --> 00:23:15,423
