484
00:23:17,623 --> 00:23:18,984
to take his ex-wife

485
00:23:18,984 --> 00:23:20,504
and kids to the hotel.

486
00:23:20,623 --> 00:23:21,984
But he doesn't even

487
00:23:21,984 --> 00:23:23,143
come downstairs

488
00:23:23,143 --> 00:23:24,264
to check on you

489
00:23:24,264 --> 00:23:25,464
for a second.

490
00:23:26,823 --> 00:23:28,264
But to be honest,

491
00:23:28,383 --> 00:23:30,224
I'd find him weird

492
