493
00:23:33,064 --> 00:23:35,064
Alright, stop nagging her.

494
00:23:38,823 --> 00:23:39,823
Xiaojiao.

495
00:23:40,944 --> 00:23:41,785
Your auntie

496
00:23:41,785 --> 00:23:43,264
