540
00:25:24,304 --> 00:25:25,304
Xiaojiao.

541
00:25:26,383 --> 00:25:27,583
I stand by what I said.

542
00:25:28,944 --> 00:25:30,823
Put your hand on your belly.

543
00:25:31,143 --> 00:25:33,103
