546
00:25:41,583 --> 00:25:43,183
But he ruined my life.

547
00:25:43,903 --> 00:25:44,904
I really hoped

548
00:25:44,904 --> 00:25:47,064
to have a child with Qian Hao.

549
00:25:47,304 --> 00:25:48,305
What does it

550
00:25:48,305 --> 00:25:49,823
have to do with this child?

551
00:25:50,423 --> 00:25:52,224
He was involved into this

552
00:25:52,224 --> 00:25:53,224
