00:26:59,143 --> 00:27:00,143
Honey, calm down.

580
00:27:00,383 --> 00:27:01,184
Calm down.

581
00:27:01,184 --> 00:27:02,343
Xia Chungeng, let go.

582
00:27:02,343 --> 00:27:03,343
