00:39:19,783 --> 00:39:20,783
Sit down.

875
00:39:21,103 --> 00:39:21,865
So many dishes.

876
00:39:21,865 --> 00:39:23,583
I thought my daughter

877
00:39:23,583 --> 00:39:25,183
would never come back.

878
00:39:25,984 --> 00:39:27,183
I missed you so much.

879
00:39:34,424 --> 00:39:36,120
(Mei Chengyi)
(I suggest you take a shower)

880
00:39:36,120 --> 00:39:36,920
(and get changed.)

881
00:39:37,016 --> 00:39:38,303
(I meant to tell you last time)

882
00:39:38,544 --> 00:39:40,303
(that you smelled like incense)

883
00:39:40,303 --> 00:39:41,384
(and burnt paper.)

884
00:39:44,183 --> 00:39:45,183
Honey.

885
00:39:45,904 --> 00:39:46,865
What are you cooking

886
00:39:46,865 --> 00:39:47,904
on the stove?

887
00:39:48,303 --> 00:39:49,224
Why do I smell

888
00:39:49,224 --> 00:39:50,623
smoke and fire?

889
00:39:51,824 --> 00:39:53,024
I don't smell anything.

890
00:39:55,303 --> 00:39:55,864
Yeah.

891
00:39:55,864 --> 00:39:56,663
Well, Dad,

892
00:39:56,743 --> 00:39:58,024
I went to see You Xin today

893
00:39:58,024 --> 00:39:59,263
and burnt an incense.

894
00:40:00,864 --> 00:40:01,864
Okay.

895
00:40:02,504 --> 00:40:03,264
I'm all sweaty.

896
00:40:03,264 --> 00:40:04,424
I'll take the shower first.

897
00:40:04,623 --> 00:40:05,864
Dinner is almost ready.

898
00:40:05,864 --> 00:40:06,425
I'll be quick.

899
00:40:06,425 --> 00:40:07,583
Take a shower later.

900
00:40:07,743 --> 00:40:08,623
Dami didn't mean it.

901
00:40:08,623 --> 00:40:09,623
You know?

902
00:40:12,743 --> 00:40:13,824
(Mei Chengyi)
(I'm home.)

903
00:40:13,904 --> 00:40:14,904
(Is everything okay?)

904
00:40:15,384 --> 00:40:16,263
(Not at all.)

905
00:40:16,344 --> 00:40:17,344
(It's terrible.)

906
00:40:19,001 --> 00:40:20,248
(Xu Kaixin recalled a message.)

907
00:40:24,024 --> 00:40:25,384
Dad, I'm going to the bathroom.

908
00:40:25,384 --> 00:40:26,384
Okay, go ahead.

909
00:40:35,103 --> 00:40:36,103
Who is it?

910
00:40:36,783 --> 00:40:37,783
Mei Chengyi?

911
00:40:40,024 --> 00:40:41,904
Xiaomi, come here.

912
00:40:41,984 --> 00:40:42,984
Come on.

913
00:40:43,384 --> 00:40:44,623
Sit down. Be good.

914
00:40:45,464 --> 00:40:46,464
It's okay.

915
00:40:46,623 --> 00:40:48,464
Alright, stop crying.

916
00:40:48,824 --> 00:40:50,263
Stop crying, baby.

917
00:40:51,143 --> 00:40:52,143
Hello.

918
00:40:53,143 --> 00:40:54,864
You've never sounded so down.

919
00:40:55,223 --> 00:40:56,504
You're having a hard time.

920
00:40:57,024 --> 00:40:57,824
What message

921
00:40:57,824 --> 00:40:58,824
did you take back?

922
00:40:59,544 --> 00:41:00,104
I'd hate

923
00:41:00,104 --> 00:41:01,623
to dump my bad mood on you.

924
00:41:01,743 --> 00:41:03,024
So I took it back.

925
00:41:03,984 --> 00:41:05,984
If you don't even tell me your problems,

926
00:41:07,143 --> 00:41:08,144
what's the point

927
00:41:08,144 --> 00:41:09,263
of being family partners?

928
00:41:12,024 --> 00:41:13,504
My ex-husband is going crazy.

929
00:41:13,864 --> 00:41:14,623
His mom is dying

930
00:41:14,623 --> 00:41:15,624
and wants to

931
00:41:15,624 --> 00:41:16,984
pass on the "throne".

932
00:41:17,103 --> 00:41:18,143
So he's asking

933
00:41:18,143 --> 00:41:19,464
for Xiaomi's custody.

934
00:41:20,904 --> 00:41:21,703
Where are you?

935
00:41:21,703 --> 00:41:22,703
I'll come over.

936
00:41:24,263 --> 00:41:25,263
I...

937
00:41:25,623 --> 00:41:27,223
I'm close to the hospital.

938
00:41:27,464 --> 00:41:28,623
Don't come over.

939
00:41:28,783 --> 00:41:29,784
I don't want you

940
00:41:29,784 --> 00:41:30,824
to fight.

941
00:41:31,024 --> 00:41:32,743
Leave this to me.

942
00:41:32,743 --> 00:41:33,424
I will tell you

943
00:41:33,424 --> 00:41:34,424
once I sort it out.

944
00:41:35,544 --> 00:41:36,623
Okay, then.

945
00:41:37,263 --> 00:41:38,025
Call me

946
00:41:38,025 --> 00:41:39,183
whenever you need me.

947
00:41:39,464 --> 00:41:40,464
Alright.

948
00:41:40,544 --> 00:41:41,864
Talk later. Bye.

949
00:42:03,583 --> 00:42:04,384
Hello, Ms. Li.

950
00:42:04,384 --> 00:42:05,424
Mei Chengyi.

951
00:42:05,424 --> 00:42:06,824
What are you up to?

952
00:42:07,344 --> 00:42:09,143
No one could reach you the whole day.

953
00:42:09,143 --> 00:42:10,544
Show some respect

954
00:42:10,544 --> 00:42:11,663
for your job and superior.

955
00:42:11,984 --> 00:42:13,303
Ms. Li, I'm really sorry.

956
00:42:13,303 --> 00:42:14,303
I left my phone

957
00:42:14,303 --> 00:42:15,065
at home.

958
00:42:15,065 --> 00:42:16,424
I just came home.

959
00:42:16,783 --> 00:42:17,583
Chengyi.

960
00:42:17,703 --> 00:42:19,344
It's a critical period.

961
00:42:19,344 --> 00:42:20,504
Everyone is busy.

962
00:42:20,504 --> 00:42:21,783
And you left your phone...

963
00:42:22,583 --> 00:42:23,623
L-Listen.

964
00:42:24,024 --> 00:42:24,984
Come to my office

965
00:42:24,984 --> 00:42:25,984
tomorrow morning.

966
00:42:26,103 --> 00:42:26,905
Alright.

967
00:42:26,905 --> 00:42:28,904
See you tomorrow, Ms. Li.

968
00:42:29,344 --> 00:42:30,344
And...

969
00:42:30,544 --> 00:42:31,544
Hello.

970
00:42:36,864 --> 00:42:37,864
What...

971
00:42:41,024 --> 00:42:41,624
It's okay.

972
00:42:41,624 --> 00:42:42,824
Three, two, one.

973
00:42:46,183 --> 00:42:47,183
You told him?

974
00:42:47,384 --> 00:42:48,384
What did he say?

975
00:42:48,904 --> 00:42:50,143
He wanted to come over.

976
00:42:50,143 --> 00:42:51,263
But I told him not to.

977
00:42:51,583 --> 00:42:52,783
He should have come over.

978
00:42:52,904 --> 00:42:54,303
Why did he ask for permission?

979
00:42:54,944 --> 00:42:56,783
He has two kids at home.

980
00:42:56,984 --> 00:42:58,583
Besides, he is busy with work.

981
00:42:58,783 --> 00:42:59,704
It only bothers you

982
00:42:59,704 --> 00:43:01,263
if you think that way.

983
00:43:01,504 --> 00:43:02,144
When did you

984
00:43:02,144 --> 00:43:03,344
become so understanding

985
00:43:03,344 --> 00:43:04,464
like a love coach?

986
00:43:32,208 --> 00:43:38,663
♪A river connects
the two ends of the city♪

987
00:43:39,510 --> 00:43:45,598
♪A lamp illuminates the day and night♪

988
00:43:46,262 --> 00:43:52,688
♪A memory marks the passage of time♪

989
00:43:53,782 --> 00:43:59,702
♪Always half lost, half happy♪

990
00:44:01,174 --> 00:44:07,569
♪Who is not struggling yet optimistic♪

991
00:44:08,361 --> 00:44:14,602
♪Whose life is not lively yet lonely♪

992
00:44:15,350 --> 00:44:22,245
♪Whose story is intense yet ordinary♪

993
00:44:22,870 --> 00:44:31,958
♪Always half perfunctory, half sincere♪

994
00:44:32,733 --> 00:44:40,281
♪How many of us
have wandered through the chaos♪

995
00:44:41,204 --> 00:44:47,318
♪How many nights
have you seen thunder and lightning♪

996
00:44:47,574 --> 00:44:55,282
♪Looking left and right throughout time♪

997
00:44:55,670 --> 00:45:01,473
♪I luckily turned the tide
when I met you♪

998
00:45:02,110 --> 00:45:09,308
♪If youthful courage
had never been exhausted♪

999
00:45:10,257 --> 00:45:16,598
♪Fearless simplicity
wouldn't have become a regret♪

1000
00:45:16,726 --> 00:45:24,369
♪In our long story,
nothing is a coincidence♪

1001
00:45:24,759 --> 00:45:29,746
♪The sky is always half night♪

1002
00:45:30,217 --> 00:45:34,678
♪Half dawn♪
